europeana:record.dc:description: This is the fifth compilation of Microlepidoptera collected in The Netherlands, covering the years 1988-1991. Seven species are recorded for the first time from The Netherlands: Elachista subocellea and Cosmiotes stabilella (Elachistidae), Teleiodes flavimaculella (Gelechiidae), Epiblema cnicicolana and Dichrorampha consortana (Tortricidae) and Eccopisa effractella and Etiella zinckenella (Pyralidae). Mompha lacteella has to be removed frorn the Dutch list, because the only record of this species was based on a misidentification of a specimen of M. propinquella.
